\caption{ (Color online) Band structure of a 20-unit-cell-thick slab of BaTaS$_3$ with \{-110\} faced.(a) Surface bands highlighted by the thickness and color of the lines scaled by the weight of surface contribution to the eigenstates. (b) Surface local density of states at different Fermi energies, E$_F$ = 0.0 eV (left), 0.18 eV (middle) and 0.27 eV (right).
\label{fig:edge} }
